title: DAZ3D - Haven for The Girl 7
description:
Haven for The Girl 7 brings a breath of fresh air to your Daz Studio Library! Haven, who is made especially for The Girl 7 is a sweet faced beauty that you will love to create with. Her morph was fined tuned to give enough realism for everyday art, yet still captures the timeless beauty and spunk of The Girl that all Daz Studio figure lovers have come to admire over the years. We just know that as soon as you get her unpacked and into your library, you'll wonder what you ever done without her.

What's Included and Features

Haven (.DUF)
Character Preset
Shaping Presets
Head Apply/Remove
Body Apply/Remove
Lashes Long/Reset
Nails Longer/Reset
Navel Apply/Remove
Nipples On/Off
Material Presets:
Base Skin
Anatomical Elements
7 Eye Colors
1 Eyelashes
7 Lip Colors + 1 Natural Lips
14 Makeup Options + 1 Natural Face
Textures Include:
28 Texture, Bump, Reflection and Sub-Surface Scatter Maps (4096 x 4096)
06 Texture and Specular Maps (4000 x 4000)
14 Texture, Bump, Normal and Specular Maps (3000 x 3000)
11 Texture, Bump and Specular Maps (2048 x 2048)
01 Transparency Map (2000 x 2000)
01 Normal Map (1024 x 1024)
This product uses the Genesis 3 Base Female UV Maps
Daz Studio 3Delight Material Presets (.DUF)
Daz Studio Iray Material Presets (.DUF)
